et" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们从您那里得到的地方不能虚假旗帜并认真对待。一旦数字出现，就不要等待歌曲“图表”声明。用您的DSP说<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f937-1f3fe-200d-2642-fe0f.png" alt="🤷🏾‍♂️" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/iqKZnAiQOj">pic.twitter.com/iqkznaiqoj</a></p><p> -  DJHED（@djhed） <a href="https://twitter.com/DJHed/status/1781100139568067005?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年4月18日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>然后，德雷克（Drake）在音乐博客作者阿卡德米克斯（Akademiks）的一篇文章下发表了评论，介绍了Hed的推文，并告诉粉丝“将[他]用作&#39;他们没有掉落的按钮”。</p><p> HED保持了唱片的直截了当，并指出“我们来自哪里，您不能假国旗并认真对待”  - 推断Lamar正在等待Drake自己确认“俯卧撑”的真实性。他补充说：“不要等待歌曲“图表”一旦数字出现。用您的DSP说。”</p><p>他在最初的推文中将拉马尔的经理安东尼·萨利赫（Anthony Saleh）称为“蚂蚁”  - 其他人在网上取笑。在整个星期中，德雷克（Drake）在他的Instagram故事中一直在分享萨利赫（Saleh）的照片，首先将缩放的自拍照与经理到明星的自拍照标题：“奇迹是今天”。另一个锯萨利赫（Saleh）站在一家OVO商品店里，该商店的标题为“我们到了袋子还是nah？”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">德雷克（Drake）刚刚在Instagram的“安东尼·萨利赫（Anthony Saleh）”上发布了肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的经理的自拍照，乌龟表情符号诱饵肯德里克（Kendrick）放弃了他的回应<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62e.png" alt="😮" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/WAS4GIowM1">pic.twitter.com/was4giowm1</a></p><p> - <a href="https://twitter.com/itsavibe/status/1780204864573673753?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年4月16日，</a>声音（@itsavibe） </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">德雷克继续对肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）施加压力<a href="https://t.co/etv1juDsXE">。</a></p><p> -  hiphopdx（@hiphopdx） <a href="https://twitter.com/HipHopDX/status/1781024669220642891?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年4月18日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>粉丝们认为，当一首名为“ One Shot”的歌曲在线泄漏时，Lamar对Drake做出了回应。曲目原来是假的，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-producer-reveals-process-behind-viral-ai-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-drake-push-ups-3619020">Tiktok说唱歌手Sytherapper透露他</a>使用<a href="/tag/ai">AI</a>创建了它。 “我震惊了自己，”他说。 “我认为人们将能够说这是假的，但人们确实认为这是真实的。”</p><p>然而，<a href="/artists/rick-ross">里克·罗斯（Rick Ross）</a>与同样有毒的“香槟时刻”（Champagne Moments）合法地回答了“俯卧撑”。在这首歌中，迈巴赫音乐集团首席执行官指责德雷克（Drake）获得了鼻子工作，并向法国蒙大拿州（French Montana）派出了停止和裁员。后者后来<a href="https://www.xxlmag.com/drake-french-montana-cease-and-desist/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">被其标签老板Gamma首席执行官拉里·杰克逊（Larry Jackson）确认。</a></p><p>在“俯卧撑”泄漏之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-budden-on-drake-kendrick-lamar-feud-diss-tracks-j-cole-3616045">乔·布登（Joe Budden）透露，拉马尔（Lamar）和德雷克（Drake）正在进行的说唱战可能是“核”</a> 。</p><p>他开始说：“无论您以为发生了什么说唱，这不是那样，不是那样的事情。” “我有一个很好的信息，双方都进入了展位。我对双方都听到的是它是核的。向上，起来。我听到可以说唱的人听到的。所以我想进来说猜测时间已经结束。辩论时间结束了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-taunts-kendrick-lamar-says-he-has-nothing-to-drop-in-response-to-push-ups-diss-track-3620086">德雷克（Drake）嘲笑肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar），他说，他“没有什么可落下的”，以响应“俯卧撑” diss曲目，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
谁是泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-is-tho-is-the-lucy-name-checked-on-taylor-swifts-torture-poets-poets-department-3620144?utm_source=rsce = rsss＆utm_medium = rsssssssssssssssssss＆campairpairt =在泰勒 - 武装六角式poets-department中，持续的名字检查Liberty DunworthFri, 19 Apr 2024 15:58:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3620144 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Swift提到了新专辑第二首曲目中的名字</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-is-the-lucy-name-checked-on-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3620144">在泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的“折磨诗人的部门”上，该帖子是“露西”（Lucy）的名字，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Dacus-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a>在她的最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《折磨诗人部》（Torred Poets Department）</a>中名为“露西（Lucy）”的人，粉丝们已经开始猜测那是谁。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">“酷刑诗人部”评论：一个难得的失误</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位明星的第11张录音室专辑今天（4月19日）发行，今天早上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-album-the-anthology-3619877">Swift宣布，实际上是一张双专辑，并分享了其余的曲目</a>。</p><p>自发行以来，粉丝们已经进入社交媒体表明，该唱片是关于她与演员乔·阿尔温（Joe Alwyn）的六年关系，以及她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975年</a>的主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利（Matty Healy）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-music-undergoes-streaming-rise-amid-reports-of-taylor-swift-romance-3443019">的短暂恋情</a>。</p><p>但是，正是在专辑的第二首歌《标题曲目》中，特别是一行引起了粉丝的注意，因为流行偶像继续提到了一个名为“露西”的人。</p><p>在这首歌中，斯威夫特批评了她的伴侣的“自我破坏”行为，并引用了他的“撤消”  - 一些粉丝坚信这是关于希利和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-apologises-to-ice-spice-over-offensive-podcast-comments-3433930">他臭名昭著的一系列争议</a>。</p><p>在赛道上，斯威夫特继续回忆起有关情人曾经告诉“露西”的情人，如果斯威夫特离开他，他会自杀。</p><p> “有时候我想知道你是否会和我一起把它搞砸了，但是你<em>告诉露西，</em><em>如果我离开的话，你会自杀</em>。” <em>，我们认识的每个人都知道为什么要成为，因为我们疯了</em>。”在后者中，粉丝们推测，对“杰克”的引用可能是对Swift的长期合作者和专辑制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">Jack Antonoff的</a>致敬。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="受折磨的诗人部" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HHiddAj-Dqc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>最终，粉丝似乎确信标题曲目中引用的“露西”是露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus）</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">格莱美</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">奖（Grammy</a> -Grammy -Winning Group）的三分之一，也是与Swift和Healy有联系的人。</p><p> Dacus与Healy有多年的友谊，Boygenius乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers</a>也是如此。</p><p>她与斯威夫特（Swift）的关系也来自杂物，因为后者在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“时代之旅”</a>中充当了流行偶像的揭幕战。同样，去年5月 - 在斯威夫特确认与希利的关系之后的几天里，达科斯和博伊根乌斯乐队的同伴<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）</a>都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-perform-with-boygenius-at-taylor-swift-show-in-nashville-3440067">加入了布里奇斯（Bridgers），在纳什维尔（Nashville）开场席位</a>。</p><p>希利还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-joins-phoebe-bridgers-for-taylor-swift-support-slot-3440482">德克萨斯州日产体育场的三场“时代”表演中的第二场</a>加入了布里奇斯，在她为斯威夫特开幕时，她是乐队的一部分。</p><p>最近，达克斯（Dacus）和斯威夫特（Swift）在去年2月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/2024-grammys-winners-list-3582015">格莱美颁奖典礼</a>上一起发布了图片，“午夜”歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">宣布了最新专辑的详细信息</a>。</p><p>虽然两者似乎仍然是朋友，但Dacus和Healy之间的关系似乎在近几个月来很酸。正如<a href="https://www.thepinknews.com/2024/04/19/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lucy-dacus-matty-healy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>粉红色新闻</em></a>所强调的那样，Healy <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-deactivates-twitter-after-lucy-dacus-hits-back-at-post-3502420">在歌手和词曲作者以一个关于Boygenius的笑话打电话给他之后，停用了他的X帐户</a>。</p><p> “我告诉露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus），&#39;Boygenius&#39;启发了我，[1975年的成员]乔治（George）启动了一支名为&#39;girlr **** d&#39;的新乐队，”希利（Healy）当时说道。 “我真的不经常听到她的声音。”</p><p>作为回应，达科斯通过写信：“你根本没有听到我的消息。” </p><figure id="attachment_3620149" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3620149" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3620149" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg" alt="菲比（Phoebe Bridgers），朱利安·贝克（Julien Baker）和博伊根乌斯（Boygenius）的露西·达科斯（Lucy Dacus），他是“最佳摇滚表演”奖“不够强大”的奖项，“最佳摇滚歌曲”奖“不够强大”，也是“最佳替代音乐专辑” “唱片”奖，与泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的姿势，泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift），“年度专辑”的获胜者和“最佳流行声音专辑“午夜”奖，以及“年度最佳制作人，非古典”的冠军杰克·安东诺夫（Jack Antonoff）在2024年2月4日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的Crypto.com竞技场举行的第66届格莱美奖颁奖典礼上的新闻室。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Boygenius-Swift-Antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3620149" class="wp-caption-text"> Boygenius的Phoebe Bridgers，Julien Baker和Boygenius的Lucy Dacus是“最佳摇滚表演”奖“不够坚强”的奖项，“最佳摇滚歌曲”奖“不够强大”和“最佳替代音乐专辑” award for “The Record”, pose with Taylor Swift, winner of the “Album of the Year” and “Best Pop Vocal Album” awards for “Midnights”, and Jack Antonoff, winner of “Producer of the Year, Non-Classical” in the press room during the 66th GRAMMY Awards at Crypto.com Arena on February 04, 2024 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Kayla Oaddams/WireImage)</figcaption></figure><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">a three-star review of the album, <em>NME</em> shared</a> : “&#39;The Tortured Poets Department&#39; ends up chasing its own tail with frenzied attempts to respond to critics despite Swift&#39;s current stature.”</p><p> It continued: “Swift seems to be in tireless pursuit for superstardom, yet the negative public opinion it can come with irks her, and it&#39;s a tired theme now plaguing her discography and leaving little room for the poignant lyrical observations she excels at. It&#39;s why the pitfalls that mire her 11th studio album are all the more disappointing – she&#39;s proven time and time again she can do better.</p><p> “To a Melbourne audience of her &#39;Eras Tour&#39;, Swift said that &#39;The Tortured Poets Department&#39; came from a “need” to write. It&#39;s just that maybe we didn&#39;t need to hear it.”</p><p> In other news about the album, fans have also been <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-internet-reacts-to-taylor-swift-name-checking-charlie-puth-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3619909">reacting after she gave Charlie Puth a shout out</a> in the lyrics. Previously, the singer-songwriter has declared his admiration for Swift and has often covered her songs during his shows. “This is why she&#39;s such a genius, man,” he said while performing her early hit &#39;Teardrops On My Guitar&#39; in 2021 (via <em><a href="https://people.com/taylor-swift-name-checks-charlie-puth-on-the-tortured-poets-department-8635772" target="_blank" rel="noopener">People</a></em> ).</p><p> In other news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> &#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-dessner">Aaron Dessner</a> has admitted to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-nationals-aaron-dessner-forever-grateful-as-he-speaks-out-on-working-on-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3620073">being “forever grateful” to have worked on Swift&#39;s new album</a> , and it appeared that Swift referenced Healy again, both in the track &#39;But Daddy I Love Him&#39; and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-why-taylor-swift-name-drops-patti-smith-and-dylan-thomas-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3620037">in a comparison to Patti Smith and late Welsh poet Dylan Thomas</a> .</p><p>唱片发行后，斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-international-dates-for-eras-tour-3458456">将于下个月在欧洲恢复她职业生涯的“Eras Tour”，然后于六月前往英国和爱尔兰</a>。 She is due to play <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-two-new-london-eras-shows-with-paramore-3538573">eight shows at Wembley Stadium in London this summer</a> as part of the run, with support coming from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-is-the-lucy-name-checked-on-taylor-swifts-tortured-poets-department-3620144">Who is the &#39;Lucy&#39; name-checked on Taylor Swift&#39;s &#39;Tortured Poet&#39;s Department&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
